For syncing vim plugins and settings. Uses pathogen.vim and git submudules.
see: http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/
for tutorial.

Installation:
	clone this git repository into ~/.vim
	create symlinks:
		ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
		ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

  git submodule init
  git submodule update

see http://chrisjean.com/2009/04/20/git-submodules-adding-using-removing-and-updating/
for a way to install, update and remove submodules.
